{"tid":285702,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"突發簡訊：兩毒販當街賣白粉","createTime":"2017-06-16T05:14:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-17T13:17:41.000Z","uid":13663,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7b9df034f4205d79c8db005e12c33506014b4f86","tid":285702,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T05:14:43.000Z","msg":"本報訊】油尖警區特別職務隊採取代號「征服者」的行動，於前日下午2時掩至油麻地炮台街截查兩名可疑男子，結果在其中一人身上，搜出40包懷疑海洛英，重約15克，市值12,000元。兩人涉嫌販毒，分別姓趙46歲及姓石45歲。昨凌晨零時，警方押解其中一名疑犯，返回其上海街住所搜查。警方相信他們在油麻地分科診所附近兜售毒品，將他們通宵扣查。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20121229/18116854\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20121229%2F18116854&d=kludMJKWjPXCT3dr1%2FxEz0bWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=5e42cb2d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20121229%2F18116854&h=f25aa398\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20121229/18116854</a>"},{"pid":"2ecf6a68fed597cc92f3e59aa96e1fd636d97ad1","tid":285702,"uid":12021,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T05:15:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"38fbfaea70b65cd31fa3e51c94bb0aa194aea1a2","tid":285702,"uid":103325,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T05:20:41.000Z","msg":"當街賣白粉，實捉到你啦"},{"pid":"da46327e4452ffe082e201e16a77329d435befa3","tid":285702,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T05:26:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好彩東方人當年係賣鴉片</blockquote><br />\n東方人是指？"},{"pid":"4f9fe3c147aee604bd9ddf1d8f9f40b115214085","tid":285702,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T05:27:43.000Z","msg":"冤案"},{"pid":"cda6dc4eec10137d6a78e6f95e9a7590aff9ef02","tid":285702,"uid":39215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T05:28:26.000Z","msg":"實捉到你！"},{"pid":"ac148a48016846220dd6ecdea30b8804afb81f28","tid":285702,"uid":83328,"like":0,"d